### 3. Awesome-AI-Agents-for-Healthcare (AgenticHealthAI)

**What it is:** Curated list of research papers, projects, and resources on AI agents for healthcare — including medical image analysis, EHR, counseling, drug discovery, and healthcare administration.

**Why you:** This is newer and growing. Early contributors who add real value get recognized faster. Your understanding of healthcare administration workflows and patient interaction systems is directly relevant.

**First 3 moves:**

- **PR #1:** Add 3–5 relevant papers or projects in areas you know (patient communication, healthcare authority building, clinical decision support).
- **PR #2:** Propose a new section on "AI Agents for Healthcare Marketing Compliance" or "AI for Medical Content Regulation" — a niche nobody else is covering.
- **Issue #1:** Start a discussion about clinical validation standards for healthcare AI agents.

**Repo link:** https://github.com/AgenticHealthAI/Awesome-AI-Agents-for-Healthcare

