## Tracking Your Progress

### Month 1 Targets
- 3–5 merged PRs across Tier 1 repos
- Active on at least 2 repos (watching, commenting on issues)
- GitHub profile shows consistent activity

### Month 2–3 Targets
- 8–12 total merged PRs
- At least 1 Tier 2 repo with 3+ contributions
- Recognized by maintainers (they respond to you by name, tag you in relevant issues)
- Started triaging issues or reviewing other people's PRs

### Month 4–6 Targets
- 15–20+ total merged PRs
- Invited as collaborator on at least 1 repo, OR recognized as a domain expert contributor
- Can legitimately claim "contributor to [repo name]" on applications and profiles

### Month 6–12 (Maintainer Track)
- Sustained contribution to 1–2 repos with deep involvement
- Maintainers invite you to core team / grant write access
- You're triaging issues, reviewing PRs, and shaping roadmap discussions

